# Prompts log

After completing any task, append to `docs/prompts-log/YYYY-MM.md` (current year-month).

Use the format in `AGENTS.md` (horizontal rule, timestamp heading, Prompt / Actions / Files changed / Outcome).

Do not skip logging for "small" tasks when the user asked for agent work on the repository.
